@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_duyxmh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.26
    v2 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.85 + v0 + 0.71)) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.84) * wp.exp(v1 + 0.56)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.93)) / wp.exp((v1 + 0.28 / v2 + 0.36)))
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.09) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.15)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.53) - (v0 + 0.95 - v1 + 0.70)) * wp.abs((tmp + 0.85 * v2 + 0.01)))
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
